title: Minecraft Live 2021: Vote for the next new mob!
author: Minecraft
description: Who will get your vote this year? The darkness seeking glare, the player-built copper golem, or the dancing collector allay? Tune in to Minecraft Live on October 16  at noon EDT to cast your vote and change Minecraft forever!
